          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/32746384/pexels-photo-32746384.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="USA" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 group-hover/card:scale-110" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/home/LongHaulParadise.astro:ox1kst" />
